  "body": "We validate the values provider in the user config, but not the ones that result after resolving the configuration (using our resolution and the config extenders). This is a blocker for #3323 and makes #3488 harder to do.\r\n\r\nWe should add something like `validateResolvedConfig(resolved)` after this:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/blob/a1a36f8dd03ab99e04c3edfc071eb32d6b906b39/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/core/config/config-loading.ts#L107-L109\r\n\r\nValidating the number of optimizer runs (#3488) is easy and low risk, so maybe that could be the first validation included there.",
